Y '''Santu Thomas Aquinas''' ['''Thomas of Aquin''', or '''Aquino'''] (c. 1225 &ndash; [[Marsu 7]] [[1274]]) metung yang [[pilosopu]] at [[theology|theologian]] king  [[scholasticism|scholastic]] a kaugalian, a kebaluan bilang '''Doctor Angelicus, Doctor Universalis'''.  Iya ing maimunakeng talasulung ning ausan dang  [[natural theology]], at tatang ning [[Thomism|Thomistic]] pipagaralan a  philosophy, nung nu maluat na iya ing pilosopung gagamitan ning [[Roman Catholic a Pisamban]]. Ing gawa bantug ya bilang  ''[[Summa Theologiae]]''. Metung kareng atlung pulu't atlung [[Doctor of the Church|Doctor ning Pisamban]], kikilanan de reng Katoliku bilang pekamatenakan a theologian ning Pisamban. Dakal lang [[Institutions named after Thomas Aquinas|pipagaralan a intstitusyun]] a mipalagyu kaibat na.
